EU Says Giving Italy Final Warning on Garbage Situation

-- B y   P e t e r   C h a p m a n
-- 
2011-09-29T10:26:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/eu-says-giving-italy-final-warning-on-garbage-situation.html
 The European Commission said it’s
giving Italy a final warning over the Campania waste management
situation.  “The waste crises in Naples and surrounding areas are a
particular concern, endangering human health and the environment
for several years already,” the commission said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Chapman at 
 pchapman10@bloomberg.net  